---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Fabric & Tech" description="Advanced fabric technology for medical scrubs. 4-way stretch, OEKO-TEX certified, and high-performance textile solutions.">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-24">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Engineering Comfort</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-500 mb-20 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg">At Yilong Scrubs, we believe the fabric is the soul of the uniform. Our proprietary fabric blends are engineered with advanced technology for medical professionals.</p>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-24">
      <div class="bg-white p-12 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-50 text-primary flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl mb-8">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 8V4m0 0h4M4 4l5 5m11-1V4m0 0h-4m4 0l-5 5M4 16v4m0 0h4m-4 0l5-5m11 5l-5-5m5 5v-4m0 4h-4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 italic">4-Way Stretch Technology</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-lg">Move freely without restriction. Our scrubs adapt to your body’s every movement, providing maximum range of motion for demanding shifts.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-12 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-50 text-secondary flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl mb-8">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 italic">Anti-Microbial & Odor Control</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-lg">Stay fresh through the longest shifts with advanced fiber treatments that inhibit the growth of bacteria and control odors.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-12 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl mb-8">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 italic">Reinforced Durability</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-lg">Lab-tested for 50+ industrial washes without losing color or shape. Our scrubs are built to withstand the rigors of hospital laundering.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-12 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-50 text-blue-500 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl mb-8">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 15a4 4 0 004 4h9a5 5 0 10-.1-9.999 5.002 5.002 0 10-9.78 2.096A4.001 4.001 0 003 15z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 italic">Moisture-Wicking Tech</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-lg">Advanced capillary action draws sweat away from the body to the fabric surface where it evaporates quickly, keeping you dry.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-[3rem] p-16 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 italic">OEKO-TEX® Certification</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">Safety is our priority. Every yard of Yilong fabric is certified to be free from harmful chemicals, providing peace of mind for sensitive skin during 12+ hour shifts. We meet the OEKO-TEX® Standard 100 for safety and sustainability.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
